Home » Products » Hardwood Flooring » Johnson Hardwood




Johnson Hardwood




Exotic and Domestic Johnson Hardwood Flooring
Johnson Hardwood Installation & Warranties Collections


 
Johnson Hardwood
Johnson  Hardwood Flooring continues to be one of the leading companies in exotic hardwood flooring industry.  Since our inception in 1999, we have continued to bring in a variety of wood species from around the world.  This allows us to offer a comprehensive collection of flooring products that will match any home and lifestyle. Johnson Hardwood craft each species by defining their unique graining, dramatic characteristic and beautiful coloration.
Johnson Hardwood products are recognized for their affordability and superior quality.  We offer the most worry free floors in the industry.  Each plank is precision milled and prefinished by using the most advanced manufacturing technology available in the industry.  Johnson hardwood floors are manufactured with the greatest care and backed by a warranty that assures a lifetime of satisfaction.
By combining our dedication to excellence accompanied with the most advanced manufacturing technology, Johnson has become one of the most preferred brands with today’s homeowners, builders and designers
Hardwood floors add a touch of nature to your home. There is no substitute for the warmth and beauty that a real wood floor offers. Its inherent appeals such as unique graining and coloration will be an inspiration to your creativity.
Johnson is dedicated to bring the natural beauty of real wood floor for your living spaces by offering a variety of species, colors and constructions to match your décor and inspire your imagination.


Installation & Warranties
Warranties

Johnson Residential Hardwood Warranty

Installation

Johnson Engineered Installation Guide
Johnson Solid Installation Guide



Collections
Johnson’s Alehouse is a newly introduced worn looking 1/2″ engineered flooring 7 1/2″ wide and comes in random lengths up to 7′ long. This product is a semi goss 11 step Aluminum Oxide 35 year warranty.
 Johnson Hardwood English Pub Hickory in Applejack is hand sculpted, hand carved, and hand stained by a two-step hand staining processes for a completely hand crafted floor. The 7-1/2 inch by 7 foot long planks are meant to represent the look of reclaimed wood at a fraction of the cost.
More…

Johnson Hardwood’s Euro series comes in a solid hardwood with light wire brushed finish and UV oil coating.
Johnson’s ForeverTuff Collection is exotic engineered hardwood flooring in 4 3/4″ wide planks. ForeverTuff lives up to its name with a premium 50 year limited residential finish warranty and a 10 year limited commercial finish warranty. Almost all other products on the market only have a 10 to 25 year limited residential finish warranty and a 0 to 5 year limited commercial finish warranty. These products also have a 1.6mm wear layer. Choose ForeverTuff, the industry’s most durable prefinished hardwood floors.
Johnson’s Renaissance Collection features distressed solid plank handscraped hickory, oak, and maple flooring. The elegant planks are range from 4 3/4″ wide to 4 7/8″ wide.  Planks come in random lengths from 12″ to 48″.  Choose from an array of species and colors, from dark to light tones with accented hues of scraping patterns.
Johnson’s Samoan Mahogany Collection features a range of exotic species in both solid and engineered constructions, ranging from 3-5/8″ wide. Planks come in random lengths from 11″ to 44″.
The Bamboo Series of the Johnson Villa Collection of hardwood flooring has a full line of solid bamboo products in a 3-3/4″ width. Choose from three styles of bamboo: horizontal, vertical, and strand. Each style comes in both natural and carbonized colors. Bamboo is an eco-friendly choice as the forest renew themselves quickly. The Johnson Villa Collection comes with a 25 Year Residential Finish Warranty and a Lifetime Structural Warranty.
The Heritage Series from the Johnson Villa Collection of hardwood flooring, like the Texas Series, is both distressed and handscraped for a rugged look with a lot of character. The Heritage Series shows off hickory in deep tones and 4″ wide planks. This look is easy to achieve with the easy to install click system. The Johnson Villa Collection comes with a 25 Year Residential Finish Warranty and a Lifetime Structural Warranty.
The Malibu Series of the Johnson Villa Collection is classic and simple for a hardwood flooring look that’s popular in many interiors. Engineered oak planks come in traditional colors and 3-5/8″ widths. The Johnson Villa Collection comes with a 25 Year Residential Finish Warranty and a Lifetime Structural Warranty.
